te><br />\n就算10-22平過10-18 我都會買10-18<br />\n因為有image stablizer 又係stm<br />\n一陣你買左1022 又覺得貴過慢過又吵過1018<br />\n<br />\ncanon 出支1018係自己打死自己<br />\n當年10-22研究費係唔平架<br />\n<br />\n利申：前canon用家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n反而我鍾意舊果支多D<br />\n至少感覺上啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n10 22個鏡身靚好多，同17 55差唔多，我都好鐘意。，不過10 18有is又平差唔多半，質素又拍得住1022，性價比無得輸"},{"pid":"1c33fecd6f8c00258c95daf752a5e61c5693dd04","tid":230993,"uid":92795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搵下有無師兄放二手10-22</blockquote><br />\n二手10-22貴過全新10-18喎<br />\n<br />\n你不如教佢買11-24L</blockquote><br />\n貴鏡小妹未撚得掂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算10-22平過10-18 我都會買10-18<br />\n因為有image stablizer 又係stm<br />\n一陣你買左1022 又覺得貴過慢過又吵過1018<br />\n<br />\ncanon 出支1018係自己打死自己<br />\n當年10-22研究費係唔平架<br />\n<br />\n利申：前canon用家</blockquote><br />\n考慮10 18中"},{"pid":"94d5c15060beeaba93d866ca8359c2175240bc49","tid":230993,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T18:36:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搵下有無師兄放二手10-22</blockquote><br />\n二手10-22貴過全新10-18喎<br />\n<br />\n你不如教佢買11-24L</blockquote><br />\n貴鏡小妹未撚得掂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算10-22平過10-18 我都會買10-18<br />\n因為有image stablizer 又係stm<br />\n一陣你買左1022 又覺得貴過慢過又吵過1018<br />\n<br />\ncanon 出支1018係自己打死自己<br />\n當年10-22研究費係唔平架<br />\n<br />\n利申：前canon用家</blockquote><br />\n考慮10 18中</blockquote><br />\n我都諗住入支廣角，之前睇過下1018同t116分別係星芒，同埋t116個變焦範圍細"},{"pid":"ec8d0e25b96991c2a62af67afe8ad497cc1b423f","tid":230993,"uid":92795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:37:38.000Z","msg":"上網睇到t124好似會出現error 01咁<br />\n買2手嘅話要點check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8b87e21f34cdbf72d3b8adfe5d1a7802920582","tid":230993,"uid":83536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T12:37:21.000Z","msg":"想買支Sony e mount廣角鏡<br />\n有咩建議？Budget $7000以下"},{"pid":"5c3e51e4ff51da5a8bc540ef1e9d38fd4f2b48c7","tid":230993,"uid":81440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"曾經留意過3支約2000既廣角，分別係sigma 10-20 f3.5, tokina 11-16 f2.8, Canon 10-18 f4-5.6, 用過頭2支, 可以簡單講講感覺<br />\n<br />\nSigma：焦段方便，日頭表現唔錯，廣角端雖只比tokina 闊1mm, 但實際效果會闊5-10%, 都幾明顯。由於只得3.5光圈，夜間手持效果幾差，要落腳架先OK。中間好sharp,但邊位變型幾勁，畫質亦一般。<br />\n<br />\nTokina：相對其他兩支窄啲，但又未至於有comment指好似用定焦咁誇張。夜間手持效果可接受。2.8可以用嚟影星，不過暫未試過。邊位比sigma有明顯改善。星芒好靚，收到f11已經有效果。缺點係flare真係好勁，要避開直接影光源。<br />\n<br />\nCanon: 未試過，勝在夠輕同靚生仔。畫質聞說幾好，同tokina 不相伯仲。f4+四級防震，夜間手持無問題，影星就唔得啦。<br />\n<br />\n最後賣咗sigma, 留tokina. <br />\n接受唔到sigma夜間手持仲差過用iphone"},{"pid":"80f8e1b387eef79fdcf7c24f3f20f08b2aba7f09","tid":230993,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"同樓主你一樣760D+kit<br />\n會入手10 18<br />\n有50.8"},{"pid":"b31687f4e38610738edb039ba6232e8253a1bb5f","tid":230993,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T18:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樓主你一樣760D+kit<br />\n會入手10 18<br />\n有50.8</blockquote><br />\nWhy? 我出買開野間店問過應該t116 is better，1018除左輕同平少少無咩好"},{"pid":"a560849d00a0224e4956c98cf39b85ce7f515271","tid":230993,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同樓主你一樣760D+kit<br />\n會入手10 18<br />\n有50.8</blockquote><br />\nWhy? 我出買開野間店問過應該t116 is better，1018除左輕同平少少無咩好</blockquote><br />\n有錢就t116<br />\n無錢就canon 1018<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cabd50494df9e0ff72011c956283331487ed587","tid":230993,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:14:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同樓主你一樣760D+kit<br />\n會入手10 18<br />\n有50.8</blockquote><br />\nWhy? 我出買開野間店問過應該t116 is better，1018除左輕同平少少無咩好</blockquote><br />\n有錢就t116<br />\n無錢就canon 1018<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbtw<br />\n10-18 67mm<br />\nt116 77mm<br />\n濾鏡又要另外買過<br />\n同埋10-18有4級IS防震，t116無(好似係)"}]}